        "@value": "Un-Silent Night is Choir! Choir! Choir!&rsquo;s warmest and fuzziest night ever! Imagine yourself surrounded by hundreds of other voices, making your way through an unforgettable mix of holiday classics and seasonal pop gems!"
      }
