        "@value": "https://nac-cna.ca/en/event/40682"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#title": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Storgårds & Sibelius: Winter Solstice | With the NAC Orchestra | Dec 3 - 4, 2026 | Southam Hall"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#image": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "https://naccnaca-eventimages.s3.amazonaws.com/40682/9169_nac_naco_26_27_batch1_6__large.jpg"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "A few things to know...\n\n\n\tStoke your inner fire and celebrate the upcoming winter solstice with an evening exploring the season’s icy majesty.\n\tTwo symphonies by Jean Sibelius provide the perfect introduction to the Finnish composer’s music— alternately austere and lush, shadowy and radiant.\n\n\nHailed as a national treasure in Finland during his lifetime, Jean Sibelius’s music has become synonymous with the country’s icy landscapes and the warmth of its people. In this program, Music Director John Storgårds leads the NAC Orchestra in..."
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns/fb#admins": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "728780803"
      }
    ],
