        "@value": "Get ready to hype up your evening at Zibi with Synaptik Dance Crew, as we celebrate the best of BTS in honour of their comeback and summer tour! Join us for a high-energy K-pop dance experience, where you'll learn some of the legendary boy group's most iconic moves taught by passionate local dancers! ARMYs, are you ready? \n\nDance at Zibi event series\n\nDance at Zibi is back for another season of rhythm, movement, and community. \n\nIn partnership with the Dream Community Foundation and the National Arts Centre, the 2026 edition..."
      }
    ],
